don't hook to our VCRs.

171
00:15:40,294 --> 00:15:42,088
Call over
the Young County Sheriffs.

172
00:15:42,255 --> 00:15:44,298
Ask them if they thought
to hook their cameras

173
00:15:44,465 --> 00:15:46,592
to some sort of
recording device.

174
00:15:48,886 --> 00:15:51,055
